Node.Notes: 3 possibilites for why this is accusative. First, just another grammatical problem from the author. Second, assumes an elided verb like "I saw." Third, carries over "the dragon gave" (gave that the beast would have a mortal wound that was healed as a sign to further deceive the whole earth. The third option is best in my mind, followed by the second.
